        <abstract> 
<p>Relieved by JM’s note and by his agreement on type size. Is alarmed by what the verdict [on <hi rend="italic">Variation</hi>] of JM’s friend will be. He is not a man of science. An unscientific reader would have condemned the <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>. An eminent semi-scientific man thought the <hi rend="italic">Journal of researches</hi> not worth publishing.</p> 
